title: The Real Housewives Of Beverly Hills S04E19  WEB-DL x264-RKSTR m
description:
Ep 19: Are You My Friend?
 The ladies meet for the first time since Puerto Rico, and try to decide who is friend and who is foe in the trip's wake.

The ladies have not seen each other since the dramatic fireworks in Puerto Rico, but are drawn together by a glamorous party for the Beverly Hills 100th anniversary at the world famous Beverly Hilton hotel.
